Mam really you are doing a great job 
But me apke sare lecture rotate ho reha hai 
Sai se nahi dhike mobile me 
And laptop me to bilkul bhe possible nahi hai apke lecture dhakna rotate hote hai sb lecture kab youtube open krte hai
